  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个健康科技的数据流图，核心是PatientRecords，它既是起点也是终点，形成一个闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，闭环结构。那从PatientRecords出发后，第一个处理节点是什么？是直接进入诊断引擎还是先有个中间环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "实际流程中，PatientRecords会先触发一个内部状态更新，所以我建议A到B都是PatientRecords，表示系统自检或状态标记，然后B再流向DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，A→B都是PatientRecords，然后B→C进入DiagnosticEngine。接下来诊断完成后去哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "诊断引擎分析后需要实验室验证，所以C要连到LabAnalyzer。另外为了合规，LabAnalyzer的数据必须进入HIPAA_Vault加密存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加C→D到LabAnalyzer，D→E到HIPAA_Vault。 vault之后呢？数据怎么回到患者端？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "加密存储后需要通过EMR_Sync同步到电子病历系统，所以E→F是EMR_Sync，然后F再回到PatientRecords完成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "E→F→G，G就是PatientRecords。但您提到闭环，G之后还有流向吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，这里有个细节。G之后还有H和I，都是PatientRecords，表示多阶段的内部状态流转，比如待审核、已归档，最后I还要再连回LabAnalyzer做定期复检。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下结构：G、H、I三个节点都是PatientRecords，形成链式状态机，然后I→J到LabAnalyzer。那J之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "J就是终点了，LabAnalyzer作为复检入口，不再往后延伸。整个流程是A到J共10个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，完整链路已绘制：A-B-C-D-E-F-G-H-I-J。我注意到B、G、H、I都是PatientRecords，这样设计是为了体现状态分层吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，A是初始记录，B是预处理状态，G是同步后待确认，H是已确认，I是归档锁定。这样审计时能追溯每个阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解。那LabAnalyzer出现两次，D是初检，J是复检，这个区分在命名上需要体现吗？还是保持同名？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "保持同名即可，实际系统中是同一个LabAnalyzer服务，只是调用场景不同。D是诊断触发，J是定时任务触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到。让我再核对一遍完整流向：PatientRecords自检→DiagnosticEngine→LabAnalyzer初检→HIPAA_Vault→EMR_Sync→PatientRecords待确认→PatientRecords已确认→PatientRecords归档→LabAnalyzer复检。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。这个结构覆盖了从患者建档、诊断、检测、合规存储、同步、状态流转到定期复检的完整生命周期。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "有个小问题，A→B都是PatientRecords，但图上看起来是单向箭头，实际业务中这个自检会失败吗？需要回退箭头吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不需要回退箭头。如果自检失败，流程在B节点终止，不会走到C。图上只画成功路径，异常流程另起一页。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，当前图只保留主成功场景。那最终结构确认了，10个节点9条边，PatientRecords占5个节点体现状态机，LabAnalyzer首尾呼应做双触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
